{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"orientation","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/orientation","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/background_color\">background_color</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/categories\">categories</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/description\">description</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/display\">display</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/display_override\">display_override</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/icons\">icons</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/name\">name</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/orientation\">orientation</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/prefer_related_applications\">prefer_related_applications</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/protocol_handlers\">protocol_handlers</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/related_applications\">related_applications</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/scope\">scope</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/screenshots\">screenshots</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/short_name\">short_name</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/shortcuts\">shortcuts</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/start_url\">start_url</a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/theme_color\">theme_color</a></li></ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">型</th>\n      <td>`String`</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">必須</th>\n      <td>いいえ</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p><code>orientation</code> メンバーは、ウェブサイトの最上位の<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Browsing_context\">閲覧コンテキスト</a>すべてについて、既定の向きを定義します。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> ユーザーエージェントの表示モードによっては、 <code>orientation</code> やその中の特定の値に対応していないことがあります。これらに対応することが、特定のコンテキストでは意味がないからです。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> 実行時に画面の向きを変更するには、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientation\">Screen Orientation API</a> を利用して実現することができます。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"値","title":"値","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>orientation</code> は以下の値の内の一つを取ることができます。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>any</code></li>\n  <li><code>natural</code></li>\n  <li><code>landscape</code></li>\n  <li><code>landscape-primary</code></li>\n  <li><code>landscape-secondary</code></li>\n  <li><code>portrait</code></li>\n  <li><code>portrait-primary</code></li>\n  <li><code>portrait-secondary</code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: json notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">\"orientation\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"portrait-primary\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/manifest/#orientation-member","title":"Web Application Manifest"}],"query":"html.manifest.orientation"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"html.manifest.orientation","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/orientation/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"値","id":"値"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"}],"summary":"orientation メンバーは、ウェブサイトの最上位の閲覧コンテキストすべてについて、既定の向きを定義します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"orientation","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"orientation","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/manifest/orientation","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/manifest/orientation/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest","title":"ウェブアプリマニフェスト"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Manifest/orientation","title":"orientation"}],"pageTitle":"orientation - ウェブアプリマニフェスト | MDN","noIndexing":false}}